the booklet is blue with indian government sign and the embassy will then paste an endorsement in your passport. hence after getting it, you can fly to india as many times as you want without wasting your time for acquiring visa. even you can stay in india for as long as you intend to. for more details, check out oci or better visit indian embassy/mission in your country. there are other categories for specialised purposes [4]. the missionary visa is mandatory for anyone who is visiting india "primarily to take part in religious activities". this rule is meant to combat 